    <item>
      <title>新泽西州美国梦债券持有人将获得补助金支持的债务偿付</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/nj-american-dream-bondholders-to-get-paid-on-grant-backed-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为资助在新泽西州梅多兰兹建造美国梦大型购物中心而出售的 2.87 亿美元市政债券的持有人将在连续两年未付款后于下周收到逾期利息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/nj-american-dream-bondholders-to-get-paid-on-grant-backed-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 17:30:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>道明银行称，随着降息的实施，加拿大房地产投资信托基金将迎来复苏</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/reits-in-canada-set-to-recover-as-rate-cuts-reign-td-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[道明考恩银行 (TD Cowen) 表示，随着投资者对北美短期降息的信心增强，加拿大房地产投资信托基金有望反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/reits-in-canada-set-to-recover-as-rate-cuts-reign-td-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 17:23:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
